      "code": "```\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\nfrom hypothesis import given, strategies as st\napp = FastAPI()\n\ngiven(x=st.lists(st.integers(), min_size=3), y=st.lists(st.floats()))\ndef test_add(x, y):\n    assert sum(x) + sum(y) == sum([z for z in x+y if z >= 0])\napp.test_route('GET', '/test-add', test_add)\n``"
